at makes ye happy, Jaranna, but listen tae the others.  Vivienne and her people are nae but trouble.  They ain't worthy of ye&quot;<br><br>&quot;Still, it's your choice&quot;  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=20371A><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/uwardenn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wardenn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/ring20.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#660000>(8/28/02 2:38:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fcircleofsistersfrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=267.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: An announcement</span><hr size=1> Warden blinks, his eyes going wide. Thus far he had been unable to say anything. He watched as Kelthalas made his comments and left. Listend to Nullo and her comments as well. About a millions thoughts flew through his mind untill he managed..<br><br>&quot;But she wanted to eat me for dinner Jar..&quot; in a weak voice.<br><br>Looking around at the shocked face, Warden decided to just stay quiet. He had met Viv a single time and she seemed to <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> ooze</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> evil. He might have been wrong, he was wrong alot. Picking up his glass of chilled berry juice, Warden leaned back in his seat, waiting for the others to respond/ <p>Warden Wildrunner<br>Scout of Bristlebane<br>Clan of Brothers<br>"Shadows are our allies, in darkness we find solace." Bikbuz Fizzledirk</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=20371A><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/uladykry.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lady Kry</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Initiate Sister </span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#660000>(8/28/02 2:51:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pu